Painted one of my FAVORITE pictures of me and my mom for Mother’s Day this year. As a little girl I used to grab her face and go in for a big smooch 😚
Now that I’ve spent some time with the painting I can’t decide if it’s done or not. Part of me wants to really keep working the details / make the colors more complex and part of me likes the rawness and how it’s kind of underworked right now. What do you guys think?
